caption.title: Example model fits and estimates of key parameters using a particle filter.
caption.p:
Model fits compared to the observations are shown for A(H1N1) (A), A(H3N2) (B), and B (C). Estimates of R
0 are shown in D-F for the three influenza types/subtypes and strength of cross-immunity shown in G-L.
